34:19.925 --> 34:21.190
Bea!

34:22.761 --> 34:24.494
Ken?!

34:26.298 --> 34:28.164
Rhian?

34:28.233 --> 34:30.634
Does anyone ever actually
work at this place?!

34:30.636 --> 34:32.435
