34:32.438 --> 34:34.237
Oh! Hello, moonshine,
how can I help you?

34:34.273 --> 34:36.205
No, no. Listen.

34:36.241 --> 34:38.375
I-I have no idea where
cabin four is,

34:38.510 --> 34:40.276
Let alone if it has a view
of the water!

34:41.547 --> 34:43.580
Wow, 50th wedding anniversary?

34:44.917 --> 34:46.783
That's--

34:46.918 --> 34:48.251
You're gonna to have
to call back.

34:48.386 --> 34:50.052
(beads rattle)

34:51.390 --> 34:53.790
(thuds lightly)

34:53.925 --> 34:58.061
♪♪♪

34:58.063 --> 34:59.695
(beads rattle)

35:00.732 --> 35:02.866
(dog barks)

35:05.671 --> 35:09.739
♪♪♪

35:09.775 --> 35:11.675
- Hey, danny boy.

35:13.011 --> 35:15.011
- Oh! I was looking for you.

35:17.816 --> 35:19.349
(tools clatter)

35:20.586 --> 35:22.118
(lid creaks)

35:22.154 --> 35:23.820
(latch clicks)

35:23.955 --> 35:25.588
- We're done, right?

35:27.893 --> 35:29.992
- It's not all on you, son.

35:33.031 --> 35:34.230
- Okay.

35:35.501 --> 35:39.235
- Who you are has everything
to do with who I've been.

35:39.304 --> 35:41.838
And I haven't always
been the best father.

35:43.475 --> 35:46.209
I should've been a better
example.

35:47.979 --> 35:49.646
I should've told you
how I felt,

35:49.648 --> 35:52.115
(sighs)

35:52.117 --> 35:54.584
Instead of hiding behind
my own bong.

35:54.653 --> 35:56.319
- Dad, you really don't
have to do this.

35:56.321 --> 35:58.621
- I do, I do, yeah.

36:00.959 --> 36:02.992
- Are you okay, dad?
- Yeah, I'm-I'm fine.

36:04.663 --> 36:06.062
(sighs)

36:06.064 --> 36:08.598
What-what I'm trying
to say is...

36:08.634 --> 36:11.100
You do worry me.

36:11.136 --> 36:13.603
Keep me up nights.

36:13.639 --> 36:15.938
Sometimes make me question
my gene pool.

36:17.742 --> 36:21.744
But I need you to know,
you never, never disappoint me.

36:24.483 --> 36:27.483
I promise you, something good
is on the horizon.

36:32.290 --> 36:34.491
(footsteps recede)

36:34.626 --> 36:36.092
(seagulls cry)

36:36.094 --> 36:39.562
♪♪♪

36:39.598 --> 36:41.297
- I don't know who to be
more pissed at, lidia,

36:41.366 --> 36:43.399
For not telling us, or mom
for getting us into this mess

36:43.435 --> 36:45.101
In the first place!

36:45.103 --> 36:47.137
- Felicia always did the books,
I thought she was on top of it.

36:47.272 --> 36:48.371
- You never thought to ask?

36:48.440 --> 36:50.440
- This was not your problem
to solve alone.

36:50.575 --> 36:52.208
- I was trying to protect you!

36:52.211 --> 36:54.110
- Because that was worked
so well in the past!

36:54.112 --> 36:55.779
- Uh, mom, your health
is back on track,

36:55.781 --> 36:57.346
Rhian is happy for the first
time in forever,

36:57.382 --> 36:59.315
And no offence,
your boyfriend is a cop,

36:59.384 --> 37:01.284
It was a little risky to tell
you what I was doing!

37:01.419 --> 37:03.853
- Sins of the mother fall
right back on the daughter.

37:03.889 --> 37:06.122
Turning to crime?

37:06.191 --> 37:08.024
Lying about it?

37:08.026 --> 37:10.460
All in the name of protecting
our family.

37:10.462 --> 37:12.328
Well, look around, lidia!

37:12.397 --> 37:15.265
Do we look like we feel
protected?!

37:15.267 --> 37:17.366
Do you feel protected?
- No.

37:18.403 --> 37:20.202
I've never felt more alone.

37:20.239 --> 37:21.805
- Well, you're not alone now,
moron, you've dragged us

37:21.940 --> 37:23.940
Into the shit pile with you!
- And we'll dig ourselves out,

37:24.075 --> 37:25.875
Like always.
- Or die here.

37:26.011 --> 37:27.877
- Family solidarity.

37:27.913 --> 37:29.946
- There is one thing I need
to do on my own.

37:31.416 --> 37:33.716
Consider me deprogrammed.

37:33.785 --> 37:35.552
The second I get back,

37:35.687 --> 37:37.687
I'm breaking up with gale.

37:37.822 --> 37:39.689
