all the usual suspects.

38:16.762 --> 38:18.427
No one's seen her.

38:19.864 --> 38:21.764
But that's actually good news.

38:24.336 --> 38:26.870
- You know, maybe she went
out for a drive?

38:28.173 --> 38:30.206
She used to do that sometimes.

38:30.275 --> 38:32.208
Likely to get away from me.

38:33.278 --> 38:35.177
I know that now.

38:36.315 --> 38:38.013
- She's gonna be okay.

38:39.951 --> 38:41.751
Hey.

38:41.787 --> 38:43.619
You, too.

38:45.023 --> 38:47.357
(fire crackles)

38:47.359 --> 38:48.457
(waves crash)

38:49.661 --> 38:51.761
(fire crackles)

38:51.896 --> 38:53.630
(insects chirp)

38:57.168 --> 38:58.434
- Mom.

38:58.503 --> 39:00.770
- Big news.

39:01.873 --> 39:03.940
- Maple leaves work best
for number two?

39:04.009 --> 39:06.076
- Hmm! ( keys jingle)
(bea and lidia gasp)

39:06.211 --> 39:07.811
- We're saved!

39:07.946 --> 39:09.779
- I may have pissed on them,
but they'll still work.

39:09.815 --> 39:11.814
Let's get you to the clinic.

39:15.654 --> 39:17.553
- Wait.

39:17.555 --> 39:19.956
(fire crackles)

39:26.198 --> 39:28.097
Is there such thing as a...

39:28.166 --> 39:30.366
Reverse exorcism?

39:33.271 --> 39:34.871
You know.

39:34.873 --> 39:36.873
For the cell cluster?

39:39.678 --> 39:41.811
(fire crackles)

39:41.946 --> 39:44.680
- Yeah.

39:44.682 --> 39:47.150
I think there is.

